asterisk-chan-modemmanager (1.0.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial packaging.
  * ALSA-direct audio with automatic USB-to-ALSA device correlation
    (PortAudio removed).
  * Native MMS receive without mmsd-tng.
  * Per-modem init AT commands over a spare AT tty port.

